node.text: Crissa knows she's a champion because she never gives up and will never let anything stop her from getting where she wants to be. Show us how you #DareToBeChampion and tag @champion for the chance to be featured!

node.text:
Urban Dove was formed in 1998 to inspire and educate students in New York through the power of sports. In our 100th Year, Champion is celebrating the most interesting and passionate teams across the globe.

SHARE YOUR TEAM’S STORY:
On social media: #Champion100
